The new version of the extension includes:

- A new, on-demand ‘Edit Code’ function (Shift+Ctrl+Enter)
- Commands to generate unit tests or docs for any highlighted snippet of code
- Context-aware chat with support for adding files from multiple repos as context
- Hot-swappable LLMs, including GPT-4o and Claude 3, for Cody Pro users

The extension is available for all Cody users, and you can install it today. Read the announcement blog (https://ckymW04.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/5A+113/ckymW04/VX7Dy17MkjyXW1C5Npn3vRBpxW4CCSrm5fX0QHN3hBC6F3pxJzW7Y8-PT6lZ3kKW8XGxn33NghllW4xl8yb1FGShMW2vxkRT2vw6HHW952nVr3jF9R3W3ZxhT_1rRWB8W1SpTYH7rbvv6W4jCJ4L3dn6TlN2Fs3dRR5lVpW2Y_m3v2ktQGTN4jH6t3VZYtJMMn4nCHfkqXW7-tZc_3z_Nt-N2smdNxsrdQnW9fR97S7m0tw6VXXBV463QTTwW8N6J302jb0LMW2lMqrq6YMqB6Vw0wbX3-S6yQMnYpps4QQ6JW2Pb2qY7p0nxLW7FTmnN8qf58WW7rrJPc2rTXJlW3NWnwL5vMB03MdbkFPYflK7W1x0jXB8FJLz4W36v-YC5cKTQqf1Hpcsd04 ) for more details on everything new.

